32/*
33 * Udp protocol header.
34 * Per RFC 768, September, 1981.
35 */
36struct udphdr {
37 uint16_t uh_sport; /* source port */
38 uint16_t uh_dport; /* destination port */
39 uint16_t uh_ulen; /* udp length */
40 uint16_t uh_sum; /* udp checksum */
41};
